#: ../../deployment/nanovllm_voxcpm.rst:3 d769a2fa327b42f1bf2e2de5ba4d7257
msgid "NanoVLLM-VoxCPM"
msgstr "NanoVLLM-VoxCPM"

#: ../../deployment/nanovllm_voxcpm.rst:5 1c38bc9dd0d346829a166cddb9ba76a6
msgid "Nano-vLLM-VoxCPM is an inference engine for VoxCPM based on Nano-vLLM."
msgstr "Nano-vLLM-VoxCPM 是基于 Nano-vLLM 的 VoxCPM 推理引擎。"

#: ../../deployment/nanovllm_voxcpm.rst:7 328daaecac7742628bbf583bf1fac7d8
msgid "Repo: `a710128/nanovllm-voxcpm <https://github.com/a710128/nanovllm-voxcpm>`_"
msgstr "仓库：`a710128/nanovllm-voxcpm <https://github.com/a710128/nanovllm-voxcpm>`_"

#: ../../deployment/nanovllm_voxcpm.rst:10 3a34ba7ca8774bb3a62110937cfb9eab
msgid ""
"It provides a Python API (sync + async streaming) and an optional FastAPI "
"demo server."
msgstr "提供 Python API（同步与异步流式）以及可选的 FastAPI 演示服务。"

#: ../../deployment/nanovllm_voxcpm.rst:13 d4e0ced39ce245a09299de978fa3d4ee
msgid ""
"This runtime is GPU-centric (CUDA + Triton + FlashAttention) and does not "
"support CPU-only execution."
msgstr "该运行时以 GPU 为中心（CUDA + Triton + FlashAttention），不支持纯 CPU 运行。"

#: ../../deployment/nanovllm_voxcpm.rst:15 80065a3615194cc5bbc8150c2136cb9e
msgid "Supported VoxCPM Versions"
msgstr "支持的 VoxCPM 版本"

