msgid ""
"Nano-vLLM-VoxCPM loads weights from ``*.safetensors`` files. Your model "
"directory should contain at least:"
msgstr "Nano-vLLM-VoxCPM 从 ``*.safetensors`` 文件加载权重。模型目录至少应包含："

#: ../../deployment/nanovllm_voxcpm.rst:55 2dc9250065774d3e8945e5a05de6f945
msgid ""
"If your checkpoint only ships weights as ``.pt`` / ``pytorch_model.bin``, "
"convert it to safetensors first."
msgstr "若 checkpoint 仅以 ``.pt`` / ``pytorch_model.bin`` 形式提供权重，请先转换为 safetensors。"

