#: ../../deployment/nanovllm_voxcpm.rst:189 b6c3f86638e94b26b95a3898b2537f42
msgid ""
"Your model directory likely does not contain ``*.safetensors`` weights (some"
" VoxCPM releases ship ``.pt`` files). Use a safetensors-converted checkpoint"
" and ensure the ``*.safetensors`` files live next to ``config.json``."
msgstr ""
"模型目录可能缺少 ``*.safetensors`` 权重（部分 VoxCPM 发行版仅含 ``.pt`` 文件）。请使用已转换为 "
"safetensors 的 checkpoint，并确保 ``*.safetensors`` 与 ``config.json`` 位于同一目录。"

